The jamDevices are consider generally as devices installed per bar

The INPUTS of the JamDevices will be considered as the Inputs of the BARS.
An Input object will be used to assign signals and depending on the configuration, it will be "conecteted" to the proper 
logical device
The INPUTS are assigned in Block Inputs, because it is a fast program, at the same speed than needed

